				<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.npost.com/blog/2010/12/02/december-techfoams-%e2%80%93-121-and-1215/" title="December TechFoams – 12/1 and 12/15" rel="bookmark">December TechFoams – 12/1 and 12/15</a></h2>
		
		<div class="post-info"><span class="date time published" title="2010-12-02T16:15:11+0000">December 2, 2010</span>  By <span class="author vcard"><a href="http://www.npost.com/blog/author/npostadmin/" title="Posts by Nathan Kaiser" rel="nofollow">Nathan Kaiser</a></span> <span class="post-comments"><a href="http://www.npost.com/blog/2010/12/02/december-techfoams-%e2%80%93-121-and-1215/#comments" rel="nofollow">Leave a Comment</a></span> </div>		<div class="entry-content">
			<a href="http://www.npost.com/blog/2010/12/02/december-techfoams-%e2%80%93-121-and-1215/" title="December TechFoams – 12/1 and 12/15"></a><p><strong>See original post at <a href="\\\\\\\">TechFoam — TechFoam</a>:</strong></p>
<p>Two TechFoams in December, the first and third Wednesdays just like every month.  Join us for tech, startup, business, or whatever kind of talk or networking you want.  As usual, nPost will sponsor the first two pitchers (or maybe a pitcher and a pizza).</p>
