3/august-techfoams-84-and-818/' title='August is here, and the weather is warm, time for some beer at more startup networking.  As usual we’ll be at The Spot Off Main in Bellevue on the first and third Wednesdays (4th and 18th) starting around 6 PM. If that isn’t enough, consider attending the NWEN Pub Night on August 11th in Bellevue [&hellip;]'>August TechFoams – 8/4 and 8/18</a> <span class="rss-date">August 4, 2010</span></li></ul></div></div>
